{"tid":2146471,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有未能通過檢測口罩流通市面　口罩廠員工涉盜竊被捕","createTime":"2020-08-08T15:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T15:45:24.000Z","uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb963c2c69fb29237ed057e9b666d497fabb55ae","tid":2146471,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"警方破獲口罩盜竊案，5人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n沙田警區刑事調查隊督察鍾美琪表示，一間位於沙田石門的本地口罩廠房，上月初有9000盒口罩未能通過內部檢測，公司決定棄置，並將有問題口罩送至堆填區，但其後有員工發現這批口罩在市面上流通，於是向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查發現，有口罩廠員工於上月28號將該批口罩運出，探員星期四到口罩廠拘捕一名主管及三名倉務員，他們年齡由34至58歲，涉嫌盜竊罪。<br />\n<br />\n警方又翻查現場閉路電視及運輸出入紀錄，發現口罩送到去土瓜灣的一個貨倉，探員在今日中午突擊搜查貨倉，發現5400盒口罩，並拘捕另一名30歲本地男子，涉嫌處理贓物罪。<br />\n<br />\n警方相信一批不合格口罩會流出，部分已重新包裝成散裝，以低價在市面發售，呼籲市民小心選購。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542626-20200808.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542626-20200808.htm&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=e324be91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542626-20200808.htm&h=3bf4585f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542626-20200808.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a1b0096afb78426f977bb5443e711cb8b24ec71c","tid":2146471,"uid":158314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:05:59.000Z","msg":"係邊款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d938309b3ae396ffb98d6ff1cf73f9b4af6fa60d","tid":2146471,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:07:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8342461099183b50f33ed9abfdb99974c22f511a","tid":2146471,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/08/08/MD8RCc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F08%2F08%2FMD8RCc.png&h=3fa36205&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}